SDECFG_ALPHA_OPT
  Please select the specific type of alpha-CPU you want to optimize
  binaries for.
  You can also choose to not optimize for any specific CPU. The resulting
  binaries will run on any alpha-compatible CPU but with a significant loss
  in performance.
